        <h2>Welcome to EcoRank!</h2>
        <p>EcoRank is an app designed to help you and your community adopt sustainable habits and make a positive impact on the environment. We believe that small changes can make a big difference!</p>

        <p><strong>How it works:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Join a Crew:</strong> After signing up, you'll be placed into a team of like-minded individuals. Each team focuses on a specific area of sustainability: Carbon Reduction, Recycling, Energy Conservation, or Water Conservation.</li>
            <li><strong>Complete Challenges:</strong> Participate in a variety of eco-friendly challenges tailored to your crew's focus. Earn points for completing each challenge.</li>
            <li><strong>Log Your Activities:</strong> Track your daily sustainable actions, such as reducing water usage, recycling diligently, or using public transportation.</li>
            <li><strong>Compete and Win:** At the end of each month, the crew with the highest combined points wins exciting prizes from our sponsors!</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>EcoRank is about more than just winning. It's about:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Learning and Growing:</strong> Discover new ways to be sustainable and improve your environmental impact.</li>
            <li><strong>Connecting with Others:</strong> Meet people who share your passion for sustainability and build a community.</li>
            <li><strong>Having Fun!</strong> Engage in friendly competition and celebrate your achievements.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Ready to make a difference? Join EcoRank today!</p>
